  <name>Workspace Windows</name>
  <summary>Show windows from the current workspace in the COSMIC panel</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Workspace Windows is a COSMIC panel applet that shows the windows on the current workspace for the panel output where the applet is placed.</p>
    <p>It highlights the active window and provides quick access to focus, minimize, maximize, close, and reorder windows directly from the panel.</p>
  </description>
